6523536%3Fs%3D100&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-100 photo' height='100' width='100'/></div><div class="text"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"> <cite class="fn">Adrian L ';' </cite><a href="/cual-es-la-diferencia-entre-los-distintos-formatos-de-audio-y-cual-deberia-elegir/#comment-1284"><time datetime="2013-06-26T21:54:41+00:00">2013/06/26 at 21:54</time></a><span class="sep">/</span><a class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-1284' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-1284", "1284", "respond", "841")'>Reply</a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>La mejor opción calidad/tamaño es, para mi claro, WMA a 48kbps con frecuencia de 44100Hz, la perdida de calidad para el oído humano no es percibida y obtienes un peso ideal con misma calidad, ideal para cualquier reproductor.</p> </section></div> </article><ol class="children"><li class="comment byuser comment-author-hidden2 bypostauthor odd alt depth-2" id="li-comment-1285"> <article id="comment-1285" class="comment"><div class="comment-avatar"> <img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/08895492876c3a8160011ac0ef0c3d1c?s=100&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D100&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-100 photo' height='100' width='100'/></div><div class="text"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"> <cite class="fn"><a href="/" rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Alejandro Alcalde</a> <span> Post author</span></cite><a href="/cual-es-la-diferencia-entre-los-distintos-formatos-de-audio-y-cual-deberia-elegir/#comment-1285"><time datetime="2013-06-27T09:06:26+00:00">2013/06/27 at 09:06</time></a><span class="sep">/</span><a class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-1285' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-1285", "1285", "respond", "841")'>Reply</a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Gracias, probaré con esa configuración. Saludos.</p> </section></div> </article></li></ol></li><li class="comment ev